code: @Override public void writeTo(StreamOutput out) throws IOException {     super.writeTo(out).     out.writeLong(byteLimit).     out.writeLong(bytesWanted).     if (out.getVersion().onOrAfter(Version.V_7_0_0)) {         out.writeEnum(durability).     } }

@Override protected void metadataToXContent(XContentBuilder builder, Params params) throws IOException {     builder.field("bytes_wanted", bytesWanted).     builder.field("bytes_limit", byteLimit).     builder.field("durability", durability). }
